Interface IUserDataSourceProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleUserDataSourceProvider

    public interface IUserDataSourceProvider
    A provider of information about which external DataSources the current user has access to.
    Since:
    4.0

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Collection<DataSource> determineAvailableDataSources(Iterable<DataSource> dataSources)
      Determines whether external DataSources are available to the current user.

    • Method Detail

      • determineAvailableDataSources

        Collection<DataSource> determineAvailableDataSources(Iterable<DataSource> dataSources)
        Determines whether external DataSources are available to the current user.
        Parameters:
        dataSources - The DataSources whose availability to the current user is to be determined.
        Returns:
        The DataSources that are available to the current user, or an empty collection if none of the specified DataSources is available.
